creator: Omega Group
descriptionHtml:
Omega immo car immobilizer is a modern anti-theft device for your vehicle. From now you can also disarm it using the app.


You can still use a maintenance-free wireless transmitter or PIN code in parallel. You can pair up to 8 phones or wireless transmitters with the immobilizer.


The Omega immo app runs in the background until you close it or turn off the app's functionality. You don't even have to take your phone out of your pocket, all you need to do is get close to your vehicle and the immobilizer will automatically connect to your phone and unlock the car.


The list of supported vehicles is available at www.omega.auto.pl. Do you want to have a car secured with Omega immo immobilizer? Contact a car installer in your area.


The application is intended for use with a Omega immo car immobilizer.
descriptionShort: Omega immo car immobilizer is a modern anti-theft device for your vehicle.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
The app runs smooth with moce devices.
Some Samsung devices may experience problems with the operation of the app - we are currently solving them.
